{"tid":1576881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好再叫人辭職！邊個叫辭就係on9仔","createTime":"2019-09-17T12:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T15:10:06.000Z","uid":293242,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0eeab49112b91306cc81c222b4815d89c6aabc3b","tid":1576881,"uid":293242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:17:01.000Z","msg":"DLLM, 你地成日叫黃絲辭黨鐵，辭Popo，辭國泰，你班人係唔係short L左。<br />\n<br />\n好似岩岩出面有兄弟話有藍絲黨鐵狗打電話，搞到手足比狗圍，如果果個係黃絲，點會發生呢d事。<br />\n<br />\n狗屋入面d狗打到d手足死咁，如果有d唔係咁黑既狗，至少會打少你2野，或者阻止到強姦，如果真係有好警（可能，只係可能），佢地可以收集證據，到時煮死班仆街！<br />\n<br />\n更甚者有人係敵陣都可以通風報信！<br />\n<br />\n古時打仗都有間碟有內應啦。你成L人叫人辭職，對面無曬人，到時手足出事真係多L謝曬你地。<br />\n<br />\n最後，多謝所有仍然身處敵陣既手足，你地既付出唔會白費既！"},{"pid":"7121419b795a80e7d7e96d8cefdf41f294d73c2a","tid":1576881,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n無錯要滲透"},{"pid":"359b3459c3f8d369ca7a29444b40c1e7361cf1b4","tid":1576881,"uid":154186,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7121419b795a80e7d7e96d8cefdf41f294d73c2a","tid":1576881,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n無錯要滲透"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:27:41.000Z","msg":"雨革之後啲滲透撚 今日打人最無人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d577c5dd0dd5f73b2d5ba4720c6ba1ee3a3d8fa","tid":1576881,"uid":263391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:29:01.000Z","msg":"賺佢哋嘅錢但做佢哋啲鬼"},{"pid":"befa21daf0037d3fae9747e7fcfabde5e2c64373","tid":1576881,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"359b3459c3f8d369ca7a29444b40c1e7361cf1b4","tid":1576881,"uid":154186,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7121419b795a80e7d7e96d8cefdf41f294d73c2a","tid":1576881,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n無錯要滲透"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:27:41.000Z","msg":"雨革之後啲滲透撚 今日打人最無人性<img src